h1.font: Step2a: Establish PK of parent entity as FK in child entity

p.font: In this case SSN is the primary key of the parent entity EMPLOYEE, so it gets mapped to a foreign key Essn in child DEPENDENT.
In addition, we must include the partial identifying attribute Dependent_name as a primary key in DEPENDENT
